ning of the large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::save} — Saves data to the large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::saveFile} — 别名 OCI-Lob::import</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::seek} — Sets the internal pointer of the large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::setBuffering} — Changes current state of buffering for the large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::size} — Returns size of large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::tell} — Returns the current position of internal pointer of large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::truncate} — Truncates large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::write} — Writes data to the large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::writeTemporary} — Writes a temporary large object</li><li>{@link OCI-Lob::writeToFile} — 别名 OCI-Lob::export</li></ul> <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/book.oci8.php">OCI8</a></div></div>
