uery as an associative array</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link oci_fetch_array()} - Returns the next row from a query as an associative or numeric array</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link oci_fetch_row()} - Returns the next row from a query as a numeric array</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>   <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.oci8.php">OCI8 函数</a></div></div>
